***COMPONENTS***

-Adafruit ESP32-S3 Feather with 4MB Flash 2MB PSRAM - STEMMA QT / Qwiic
-Adafruit Electret Microphone Amplifier - MAX9814 with Auto Gain Control
-Adafruit 0.96" 160x80 Color TFT Display w/ MicroSD Card Breakout - ST7735
-LiPo 3500mAh 3.7 V battery
-mini pushbutton switch
-microSD
-two-piece PLA 3D printed housing
(jumpers, reclosable fastener tape, duct tape, double-sided gel adhesive tape, 5x7 perfboard, soldering equipment)

***PINOUT***

==Mic==
AR -> GND
OUT -> GPIO_8
GAIN -> 3V
VDD -> 3V
GND -> GND

==TFT==
Vin -> 3V
3V -> X
GND -> GND
SCK -> GPIO_36
MISO -> GPIO_37
MOSI -> GPIO_35
TFT_CS -> GPIO_9
RST -> GPIO_10
DC -> GPIO_11
SD_CS -> GPIO_12
LIT -> GPIO_13

==Button==
3V(HI) -> Button -> GPIO_6 (W/ Internal pulldown resistor)
